<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
  <title>Trading Desk ¬∑ Link Sent</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #040810;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .card {
      background: #0d1526;
      border: 1px solid #1e293b;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 40px 44px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 420px;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: #38bdf8;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 18px; }
    h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #f8fafc;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #7b8fa4;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .magic-link-box {
      background: #0a1628;
      border: 1px solid #1e40af;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation: glow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }
    @keyframes glow {
      from { box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15); }
      to   { box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3); }
    }
    .magic-link-box .label {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      color: #facc15;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .magic-link-btn {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9, #2563eb);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: opacity 0.15s, transform 0.1s;
    }
    .magic-link-btn:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    .magic-link-btn:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    .temp-notice {
      background: #1a1a0a;
      border: 1px solid #854d0e;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #fbbf24;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .info {
      background: #0f2a1f;
      border: 1px solid #166534;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #4ade80;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .back { font-size: 12px; color: #475569; }
    .back a { color: #38bdf8; text-decoration: none; }
    .back a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="logo">TRAMMO ¬∑ NH3 DESK</div>
    <div class="icon">üîê</div>
    <h1>Your Login Link</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Click the button below to sign in to the trading desk.
    </p>

    <div class="magic-link-box">
      <div class="label">‚ö° Magic Link Ready</div>
      <a href={@magic_link} class="magic-link-btn">Sign In Now ‚Üí</a>
    </div>

    <div class="temp-notice">
      ‚è≥ Email delivery is not yet configured.<br/>
      This link is shown here temporarily for convenience.
    </div>

    <div class="info">
      ‚úì The link is single-use and does not expire.<br/>
      ‚úì You can only request a new link every 5 minutes.<br/>
      ‚úì Do not share the link with anyone.
    </div>
    <div class="back">
      <a href="/login">‚Üê Back to login</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
